  "S02n222:57": "namo bhagavate vairocanāya tathāgatāyārhate samyaksaṃbuddhāya |",
  "S02n222:58": "namo bhagavate vikasitakamalottaragandhaketurājāya tathāgatāyārhate samyaksaṃbuddhāya |",
  "S02n222:59": "ebhyo namaskṛtvā imāṃ bhagavatīṃ sarvatathāgatoṣṇīṣasitātapatrā- nāmāparājitāṃ pratyaṅgirāṃ pravakṣyāmi |",
  "S02n222:60": "sarvakalikalahavigrahavivādapraśamanīm |",
  "S02n222:61": "sarvabhūtagrahanivāraṇīm |",
  "S02n222:62": "sarvaparavidyācchedanīm |",
  "S02n222:63": "akālamṛtyuparitrāyaṇīm |",
  "S02n222:64": "sarvasattvabandhanamokṣaṇīm |",
  "S02n222:65": "sarvaduḥsvapnanāśanīm |",
  "S02n222:66": "yakṣarākṣasagrahāṇāṃ vidhvaṃsanakarīm |",
  "S02n222:67": "caturaśītināṃ grahasahasrāṇāṃ vidhvaṃsanakarīm |",
  "S02n222:68": "aṣṭāviṃśatīnāṃ nakṣatrāṇāṃ prasādanakarīm |",
  "S02n222:69": "sarvaśatrunivāraṇīmaṣṭānāṃ mahāgrahāṇāṃ vidhvaṃsanakarīm |",
  "S02n222:70": "ghoraduṣṭaduḥsvapnānāṃ ca vināśanakarīm |",
  "S02n222:71": "viṣaśastrāgnyudakottāraṇīm |",
  "S02n222:72": "sarvadurgatibhayottaraṇīm |",
  "S02n222:73": "yāvadaṣṭāvakālamaraṇaparitrāṇakarīm |",
  "S02n222:74": "aparājitāṃ mahāghorāṃ mahābalāṃ mahātejāṃ mahācaṇḍāṃ mahāśvetāṃ mahadīptāṃ mahāmālāṃ mahājvālāṃ mahāpāṇḍaravāsinīm |",
  "S02n222:75": "āryatārā bhṛkuṭī caiva jayā ca vijayā tathā |",
  "S02n222:76": "sarvamāravihantrī ca vajramāleti viśrutā ||",
  "S02n222:77": "padmā bhāvajacinhā ca mālā caivāparājitā |",
  "S02n222:78": "vajratuṇḍī viśālī ca śāntā vaidehapūjitā ||",
  "S02n222:79": "saumyarūpā mahāśvetā jvālā pāṇḍaravāsinī |",
  "S02n222:80": "āryatārā mahābalā aparā vajraśṛṅkhalā ||",
  "S02n222:81": "[tathā ca] vajrakaumārī kulaṃdarī [tathaiva] ca |",
  "S02n222:82": "vajrahastā vajravidyā [tathā] kāñcanamālikā ||",
  "S02n222:83": "kusuṃbharatnā(radanā)",
  "S02n222:84": "caiva vairocanakulaprabhā |",
  "S02n222:85": "tathāgatakuloṣṇīṣaviśrutā vijṛmbhamānikā ||",
  "S02n222:86": "vajrā kanakaprabhā locanā vajratuṇḍikā |",
  "S02n222:87": "[tathā] śvetā ca kamalākṣiṇī buddhalocanā ||",
  "S02n222:88": "tathā vajraprabhā candrā tathā vajradharāpi ca |",
  "S02n222:89": "vajramālā mahāmāyā devī ca kanakaprabhā ||",
  "S02n222:90": "sulocanā [tathā caiva] śvetā ca kamalekṣaṇā |",
  "S02n222:91": "vinītā śāntacittā ca ātmaguṇajñā śaśiprabhā ||",
  "S02n222:92": "ityetā mahāmudrāgaṇāḥ sarvamātṛgaṇāśca sarvā rakṣāṃ kurvantu mama sarvasattvānāṃ ca |",
  "S02n222:93": "om ṛṣigaṇapraśaste sarvatathāgatoṣṇīṣasitātapatre hū hū hrīṃ ṣṭroṃ jambhani |",
  "S02n222:94": "hū hū hrīṃ ṣṭroṃ stambhani |",
  "S02n222:95": "om hū hū hrīṃ ṣṭro paravidyāstambhanakarī |",
  "S02n222:96": "hū hū hrīṃ ṣṭroṃ sarvayakṣarākṣasagrahāṇāṃ vidhvaṃsanakarī |",
  "S02n222:97": "hū hū hrīṃ ṣṭroṃ caturaśitīnāṃ grahasahasrāṇāṃ vidhvaṃsanakarī |",
  "S02n222:98": "hū hū hrīṃ ṣṭro aṣṭāviṃśatināṃ nakṣatrāṇāṃ prasādanakarī |",
  "S02n222:99": "hū hū hrīṃ ṣṭro aṣṭānāṃ mahāgrahāṇāṃ vidhvaṃsanakarī |",
  "S02n222:100": "hū hū hrīṃ ṣṭroṃ rakṣa 2 māṃ sarvasattvāṃśca |",
  "S02n222:101": "namo bhagavati sarvatathāgatoṣṇīṣasitātapatre mahāpratyaṅgire mahasahasrabhuje mahāsahasraśīrṣe koṭīśatasahasranetre abhedye jvalitaṭaṃkāri mahavajrodāre tribhuvanamaṇḍale |",
  "S02n222:102": "om svastirbhavatu mama sarvasattvānāṃ ca |",
