  "S02n222:428": "sarvajvarāḥ śirovartimapanayantu mama sarvasattvānāṃ ca arddhāvabhedakam,",
  "S02n222:429": "arocakam akṣirogaṃ nāsarogaṃ mukharogaṃ kaṇṭharogaṃ hṛdrogaṃ galagrahaṃ karṇaśūlaṃ dantaśūlam uraḥśūlaṃ hṛdayaśūlaṃ marmaśūlaṃ pṛṣṭhaśūlam udaraśūlaṃ vastiśūlaṃ gudaśūlaṃ yoniśūlaṃ pradaraśūlam ūrūśūlaṃ jaṅghāśūlaṃ hastaśūlaṃ pādaśūlam aṅgapratyaṅgaśūlaṃ mama cāpanayantu |",
  "S02n222:430": "bhūtapretavetālaḍākinījvaradagdhakaṇḍūkiṭībhakuṣṭapittakaplīhabhagaṃdaralūtāpāmāvaisarpaloha-",
  "S02n222:431": "liṅgāśeṣaśvāsatrāsakāsamūrchāgaraviṣayayogāgnyudakamāramārīkalahavairakāntārākālamṛtyutryambukatrai(tai)",
  "S02n222:432": "lāṭakavṛścikasarpanakulasiṃhavyāghrarkṣatarakṣucarmaramakaravṛkataskarājīvakāyikānapanayantu |",
  "S02n222:433": "anyeṣāṃ sarveṣāṃ sitātapatramahoṣṇīṣamahāpratyaṅgirāvidyānubhāvena yāvad dvādaśayojanābhyantareṇa pañcāśatayojanābhyantareṇa vā vidyābandhaṃ karomi tejobandhanaṃ karomi sarvavidyābandhanaṃ karomi paravidyābandhanaṃ karomi sīmābandhanaṃ karomi dharaṇībandhanaṃ karomi daśadigbandhanaṃ karomi parasainyastambhanaṃ karomi |",
  "S02n222:434": "tadyathā om anane 2 khakhane 2 vīṣama 2 vīre 2 maunya 2 śānte 2 dānte 2 vajradhara bandhabandhani vajrapāṇe phaṭ |",
  "S02n222:435": "om hū ṣṭroṃ phaṭ 2 svāhā |",
  "S02n222:436": "om vajrapāśe bandha 2 vajrapāśaṃ ca sarvaduṣṭavighnavināyakān hū phaṭ 2 rakṣa 2 māṃ sarvasattvāṃśca svāhā |",
  "S02n222:437": "ya imāṃ sarvatathāgatoṣṇīṣasitātapatrānāmāparājitāpratyaṅgirāmahāvidyārājñīṃ likhitvā bhūrjapatre vastre vā valkale vā kāyagataṃ vā kaṇṭhagataṃ vā kṛtvā dhārayiṣyati vāciṣyati aśuddhakaṃ na kṣamiṣyati |",
  "S02n222:438": "sarvakṛtyakarma na kramiṣyati |",
  "S02n222:439": "nagaraṃ kramiṣyati,",
  "S02n222:440": "yogaṃ kramiṣyati,",
  "S02n222:441": "nākālamṛtyunā kālaṃ kariṣyati |",
  "S02n222:442": "sarvagrahāṇāṃ sarvavighnavināyakānāṃ ca priyo bhaviṣyati |",
  "S02n222:443": "mana-āpaścaturaśītikalpakoṭīsahasrāṇi jātau jātau jātismaro bhaviṣyati caturaśītivajrakulakoṭiniyutaśatasahasrāṇi vidyādevatā nityaṃ satatasamitaṃ tasya rakṣāvaraṇaguptiṃ kariṣyanti |",
  "S02n222:444": "caturaśītivajradūtī kiṃkarā nityaṃ paripālayiṣyanti teṣāmapi priyo bhaviṣyati |",
  "S02n222:445": "mana-āpaśca na kadācidyakṣatvaṃ na rākṣasatvaṃ na bhūtatvaṃ na piśācatvaṃ na pūtanatvaṃ na kaṭapūtanatvaṃ na manuṣyadāridryaṃ pratyanubhaviṣyati |",
  "S02n222:446": "gaṅgānadībālukāsaṃkhyeyāprameyāṇāṃ buddhānāṃ bhagavatāṃ puṇyaskandhena samanvāgato bhaviṣyati |",
  "S02n222:447": "imāṃ ca sarvatathāgatoṣṇīṣasitātapatrānāmāparājitāṃ pratyaṅgirāṃ mahavidyārājñīṃ dhārayamāṇa abrahmacārī brahmacārī bhaviṣyati |",
  "S02n222:448": "amaunī maunī bhaviṣyati |",
  "S02n222:449": "aśuciḥ śucirbhaviṣyati |",
  "S02n222:450": "anupavāsī upavāsī bhaviṣyati |",
  "S02n222:451": "yo'pi pañcānantaryakārī syāt so'pi nirdhūtapāpo bhaviṣyati |",
  "S02n222:452": "pūrvakarmāvaraṇaṃ niravaśeṣaṃ parikṣayaṃ gacchati |",
  "S02n222:453": "yaḥ kaścit mātṛgrāme tathāgatoṣṇīṣasitātapatrānāmāparājitā mahāpratyaṅgirā mahāvidyārājñīṃ dhārayamāṇaḥ putrārthī putraṃ pratilabhate |",
  "S02n222:454": "āyuḥpuṇyabalaṃ pratilabhate |",
  "S02n222:455": "itaścyutvā sukhavatyāṃ lokadhātāvupapadyate |",
  "S02n222:456": "sa ca rāgadveṣamohamānadarpavigato bhaviṣyati |",
  "S02n222:457": "yaḥ kaścinmanuṣyamāre paśumāre gomāre sarve'pyupadravopasargopāyāsaparacakrāgamaneṣu tasya bhagavato jinasya samyaksaṃbuddhasya sarvatathāgatoṣṇīṣasitātapatrānāmāparājitāṃ dhvajāgrāvaropitāṃ kṛtvā mahatā pūjāsatkāreṇa mahatīṃ pūjāṃ kṛtvā sarvanagaradvāreṣu praveśayet vihāre vā grāme vā nagare vā janapade vā nigame vā śmaśāne vā parvate vā araṇyāyatane vā imāmaparājitāṃ pratyaṅgirāṃ vidyārājñīṃ mahatā satkāreṇa praveśayet |",
  "S02n222:458": "praveśitamātreṇa praśāntikṛto bhaviṣyati |",
  "S02n222:459": "sarve'pyupadravopasargopāyāsāḥ paracakrāṇi praśāmyanti |",
  "S02n222:460": "ananto nāgarājā śaṅkhapālo nāgarājā mahākṛṣṇo nāgarājā nandyupanaṃdau nāgarājānau anye ca sarve te nāgarājānaḥ kāle ca kālaṃ varṣayiṣyanti kālena kālaṃ autsukyamāpatsyate |",
  "S02n222:461": "kālena kālaṃ garjayiṣyanti sarvarogopadravāṃścopaśamayiṣyanti |",
  "S02n222:462": "om ṣṭroṃ bandha 2 sarvaduṣṭān rakṣa 2 māṃ sarvasattvāṃśca svāhā |",
  "S02n222:463": "om hū ṣṭroṃ bandha 2 duṣṭān rakṣa 2 māṃ sarvasattvāṃśca vajrapāṇe hū phaṭ svāhā |",
  "S02n222:464": "om sarvatathāgatoṣṇīṣa avalokitamūrdhni tejorāśi |",
  "S02n222:465": "om jvala 2 dhak 2 khāda 2 dara 2 vidara 2 chinte (chinda)",
  "S02n222:466": "2 bhinda 2 hū 2 phaṭ 3 rakṣa 2 māṃ sarvasattvāṃśca svāhā |",
  "S02n222:467": "om sarvatathāgatoṣṇīṣasitātapatre hū phaṭ |",
  "S02n222:468": "om rakṣa 2 māṃ sarvasattvāṃśca hū phaṭ svāhā |",
  "S02n222:469": "tadyathā- om anale 2acare 2 khasame 2 vīre 2 saumye 2 sarvabuddhādhiṣṭhānādhiṣṭhite sarvatathāgatoṣṇīṣasitātapatre sarvaduṣṭacittān hū phaṭ svāhā |",
  "S02n222:470": "buddhayogena sarvopadraveṣu trijaptā kartavyā |",
  "S02n222:471": "sarvabuddhabodhisattvāśca sadevamānuṣāsuragaruḍakinnaramahoragaśca loko bhagavato bhāṣitamabhyanandanniti |",
  "S02n222:472": "āryasarvatathāgatoṣṇīṣasitātapatrānāmaparājitā pratyaṅgirā",
  "S02n222:473": "mahāvidyārājñī samāptā ||"
}